    "attributes": {
        "action": "Every life Matters too - Mandatory Custodial Sentences for assaults of any kind",
        "additional_details": "ALL proven assaults of any kind, on civilians and civil servants alike, should be met with an automatic custodial sentence and all such sentences should be served consecutively, not concurrently, to any other sentences, if any.\r\n \r\nSentencing should after all be a real deterrent against assault and abuse, not just a mere distraction.\r\n \r\nEvery life matters.",
        "background": "\"Every journey matters to the Mayor of London and TFL\" - Well, How about a more important slogan of \"Every life Matters too\" and resolve the lawlessness in this country too!\r\n \r\nWe need tougher Policing and tougher Sentencing for all assaults of any kind, whether on the streets or inside prisons.",
